### **Core Components**
```
Context Cleaner Architecture
â”œâ”€â”€ ğŸ“Š Analytics Engine
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ ProductivityAnalyzer - Core analysis algorithms
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ TrendCalculator - Time-series analysis  
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ ImpactEvaluator - Optimization effectiveness
â”œâ”€â”€ ğŸ“ˆ Dashboard System
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Web Server - FastAPI-based interface
â”‚   â”œâ”€â”€ Data Visualization - Interactive charts
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ Real-time Updates - Live metric streaming
â”œâ”€â”€ ğŸ—ƒï¸ Data Management
